SchoolBox Our Treaty Questions And Answers Pages 14 - 19
What event happened on the 20th of March 1839?

The 1839 NZ flag was chosen ( The United Tribes Of New Zealand )


What happened on the 28th of October 1835?

The Declaration of the Independence of New Zealand was signed.


Explain how the Declaration of Independence benefited Maori.



Explain why a flag was needed in New Zealand and what the events were that caused the need for a new flag.



Why did Maori send petitions to Britain and not to other countries?
